<h3 id="tricks">Tricks</h3>

<ul>
  <li><a href="http://docs.yclas.com/eu-vat/">EU VAT</a>: Include VAT to the orders</li>
  <li><a href="http://docs.yclas.com/how-to-publish-different-contact-email/">How to publish an ad with a different contact email</a>: Publisher can be contacted on a different email than his account email address</li>
  <li><a href="http://docs.yclas.com/paypal-email-for-sellers/">PayPal email for sellers</a>: Sellers can specify the PayPal email address</li>
  <li><a href="http://docs.yclas.com/use-shipping-custom-field/">How to use shipping custom field</a>: Let sellers add the shipping cost to the price of their products</li>
  <li><a href="http://docs.yclas.com/buyer-instructions/">Buyer Instructions</a>: Sellers have the option to enter a text that will be attached to the email sent to buyers after they purchase their product</li>
  <li><a href="http://docs.yclas.com/sell-digital-goods/">Sell Digital Goods</a>: Users can upload and sell digital goods in your website</li>
</ul>

